official_title: Honoring the life and achievements of His Holiness Pope John Paul II and expressing profound sorrow on his death.
subjects: Civil rights and liberties, minority issues

summary.text: Honors the life and work of Pope John Paul II. Expresses condolences to the people of Poland for the loss of such an inspirational figure in Poland's political transformation. Extends sympathy to Catholics around the world who looked to the Pope as Supreme Pontiff. Calls upon the people of the United States to reflect on the Pope's life during the worldwide period of remembrance following his death.
